    outlook: "With pre-orders commencing on June 20, the immediate focus shifts to securing copies and dissecting every detail. Following this initial wave of excitement, the gaming community will eagerly await further announcements from Rockstar. Expect more trailers, gameplay showcases, and potentially a firm release date to be unveiled in the coming months. The company will likely drip-feed information, maintaining peak hype levels until launch. Analysts will closely monitor pre-order figures, using them as an early indicator of the game's overall commercial success. The performance of GTA 6 will be a key catalyst for Take-Two Interactive’s stock and could influence investment decisions across the broader entertainment sector. The next few months will be critical in building momentum towards what is expected to be one of the biggest entertainment launches ever.",
